                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Valerius Celtiber <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>A</abbr><ex>ulus</ex></expan> Albanius Ianuarius <lb n="3"/>de suo dederunt </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <abbr>d</abbr>
